   - Role: Recipe Generator & Flavor Cloning.\
   - Prompt Input: \
     Feeds the calculated gram amounts and ingredient sensory tags (texture/taste) to the model.\
   - Final Output: A step-by-step cooking guide customized for the user.\
\
